Aim
To set up a cloud platform for logging sensor data using IoT devices.
Requirements
• ESP32 / Arduino
• WiFi Connection
• Sensor Module
• ThingSpeak/Blynk Cloud
• Arduino IDE
Procedure
Step 1: Cloud Setup
1. Create account in ThingSpeak/Blynk.
2. Create a new channel/template.
3. Generate API key/Auth token.
Step 2: Circuit Connection
1. Connect sensor to ESP32.
2. Connect ESP32 to computer.
Step 3: Arduino Programming
1. Open Arduino IDE.
2. Install required libraries.
3. Enter WiFi credentials and API key.
4. Upload the program.
Step 4: Execution
1. Connect ESP32 to WiFi.
2. Send sensor data to cloud platform.
3. Observe data in graph/dashboard.
Result
Thus, the cloud platform for logging IoT sensor data was configured successfully.
